    <title>To require that overseas contingency operations be paid for.</title>
    <relatedBills />
    <cosponsors />
    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. RANGEL:H.R. 1510.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following: Article XVI of the Constitution--Congressshall have power to lay and collect taxes on incomes....[Page H1805]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
